WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.430
Welcome and good evening, everybody.

00:00:05.440 --> 00:00:08.830
I know it's late, so let's go over what

00:00:08.840 --> 00:00:11.550
the Lord showed us yesterday. Yesterday

00:00:11.560 --> 00:00:12.710
was heavy;

00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:16.070
we were in the Spirit.

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:21.550
I saw the boils on the

00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:24.190
people, and they were massive—the size of half-dollars. Some of them were

00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:26.110
the size of quarters, and some

00:00:27.880 --> 00:00:30.670
like dimes. There were boils on

00:00:30.680 --> 00:00:32.350
all their skin, and they looked like

00:00:32.360 --> 00:00:34.110
they were filled with some kind of

00:00:34.120 --> 00:00:35.830
fluid.

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:37.830
It looked almost like the membrane

00:00:37.840 --> 00:00:38.990
when you touch a

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:41.150
stove and get a burn on your

00:00:41.160 --> 00:00:43.950
hand, like a blister.

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:50.470
That's what this looked like on the

00:00:50.480 --> 00:00:52.510
people I saw in New

00:00:52.520 --> 00:00:54.950
York.

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:57.150
What I thought was interesting was that it

00:00:57.160 --> 00:00:59.830
was on their mouths, in their mouths, and on their throats. In the vision,

00:00:59.830 --> 00:00:59.840
I went inside the body and could see that

00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:02.470
it was on their physical throat

00:01:02.470 --> 00:01:02.480
and

00:01:02.480 --> 00:01:04.910
inside.

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:16.190
Then I saw

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:18.510
a blackout.

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:21.790
I kept hearing 'darkness,'and it was

00:01:21.800 --> 00:01:25.430
cold. I could

00:01:25.440 --> 00:01:28.310
see the buildings in New York in this

00:01:28.320 --> 00:01:30.710
vision, and all the buildings were

00:01:30.720 --> 00:01:32.670
blacked out

00:01:32.670 --> 00:01:32.680
with

00:01:32.680 --> 00:01:34.990
no power on.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:38.110
As there was no power, I saw people

00:01:38.120 --> 00:01:41.750
with 50-gallon drums,

00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:44.350
putting fires in them to keep

00:01:44.360 --> 00:01:45.990
warm.

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:48.430
They had scarves and hats on—the

00:01:48.430 --> 00:01:48.440
kind

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:50.310
that pull over your

00:01:50.310 --> 00:01:50.320
ears—and

00:01:50.320 --> 00:01:51.990
they had these coats on,

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.390
keeping themselves warm

00:01:54.390 --> 00:01:54.400
by

00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:56.870
these 50-gallon drums.

00:01:56.880 --> 00:01:58.990
I was praying into that, but

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:01.310
then I saw people in the background with

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:03.910
buildings on fire,

00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:08.790
and they were looting what they could.

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:11.590
As I panned out

00:02:11.600 --> 00:02:16.070
through the lens, I could see Toronto,

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:18.830
and it spread from Toronto all the way

00:02:18.840 --> 00:02:22.070
down to Miami.

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:23.670
Sorry, I was around some mold today

00:02:24.680 --> 00:02:26.950
and I'm coughing a little bit,

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:29.030
but all is well.

00:02:29.040 --> 00:02:31.270
I've got this; it's not a virus, it's

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:34.390
because of the mold. I hate mold.

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:37.830
I saw it

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:39.750
go all the way down the East Coast,

00:02:39.750 --> 00:02:39.760
and

00:02:39.760 --> 00:02:42.150
as I saw this, I saw mass migration

00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:43.510
again;

00:02:43.520 --> 00:02:48.390
people were leaving.

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:51.430
I saw a massive

00:02:51.430 --> 00:02:51.440
white

00:02:51.440 --> 00:02:54.270
medical ship with a huge red

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:58.470
cross on it

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:03.110
parked outside of New York.

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:05.830
The hospitals were full, and they were

00:03:05.840 --> 00:03:07.430
transporting

00:03:07.430 --> 00:03:07.440
people

00:03:07.440 --> 00:03:11.150
by helicopter and other ways to this big

00:03:11.160 --> 00:03:14.070
boat.

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:19.870
The ship was docked,

00:03:19.880 --> 00:03:22.590
but people were being transported

00:03:22.600 --> 00:03:24.270
to

00:03:24.270 --> 00:03:24.280
it,

00:03:24.280 --> 00:03:26.990
which I thought was interesting

00:03:26.990 --> 00:03:27.000
because

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:29.190
you only take a

00:03:29.200 --> 00:03:31.590
helicopter ride if it's very

00:03:31.600 --> 00:03:33.550
serious and you're not about to make it.

00:03:33.560 --> 00:03:34.790
They don't give you a

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:36.070
helicopter ride just to give you a

00:03:36.080 --> 00:03:37.630
helicopter ride.

00:03:37.640 --> 00:03:40.950
The other part was

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:42.470
I saw

00:03:43.440 --> 00:03:45.470
a mime.

00:03:45.480 --> 00:03:48.950
I saw a white-faced clown

00:03:48.960 --> 00:03:53.070
with blackest mascara around

00:03:53.080 --> 00:03:54.430
his eyes

00:03:54.440 --> 00:03:57.030
and

00:03:57.030 --> 00:03:57.040
teardrops—the

00:03:57.040 --> 00:04:00.630
small part of

00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:02.150
a teardrop that would drop

00:04:02.160 --> 00:04:03.870
on your cheek, kind of like what

00:04:03.870 --> 00:04:03.880
gang

00:04:03.880 --> 00:04:06.230
members do. This

00:04:06.240 --> 00:04:08.670
was a massive teardrop that started at

00:04:08.680 --> 00:04:12.470
the top and went down like

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:15.630
this; it had a black liner

00:04:15.640 --> 00:04:17.550
and white in the middle, and his eyes

00:04:17.550 --> 00:04:17.560
were

00:04:17.560 --> 00:04:20.229
blacked out.

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:25.030
This was on both eyes.

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:28.230
He was wearing a black and white

00:04:28.240 --> 00:04:31.430
outfit with a

00:04:34.280 --> 00:04:37.670
hat like Laurel and Hardy wear;

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:39.590
it was

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:41.870
a circle with a little dome,

00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:46.150
a white band around it,

00:04:46.150 --> 00:04:46.160
and

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:49.710
a flower coming off the side.

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:53.270
He was making a

00:04:53.270 --> 00:04:53.280
bent-over

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:56.270
motion and was

00:04:56.280 --> 00:04:59.910
crying without sound—a mime.

00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:01.430
He

00:05:01.430 --> 00:05:01.440
looked

00:05:01.440 --> 00:05:03.830
like he was sobbing and

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:06.950
making a noise, but with no sound. If you were to put noise to

00:05:06.950 --> 00:05:06.960
it, it

00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:09.230
would be

00:05:09.240 --> 00:05:10.710
a

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:13.070
travail

00:05:13.070 --> 00:05:13.080
cry.

00:05:13.080 --> 00:05:14.830
I know that was symbolic;

00:05:14.840 --> 00:05:16.550
there's something to this.

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:18.870
Not everything is black and

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:20.030
white;

00:05:20.040 --> 00:05:21.990
it's a metaphor. That's what

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:24.910
I'm trying to tell you. Then I saw

00:05:24.920 --> 00:05:27.190
dogwood trees

00:05:27.200 --> 00:05:30.430
and I heard 'dogwood,

00:05:30.440 --> 00:05:32.230
dogwood.'I

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:34.430
knew it was symbolic of something

00:05:34.440 --> 00:05:37.350
else. A lot

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:38.590
of you are

00:05:38.600 --> 00:05:40.790
researchers, and you say, Brandon,

00:05:40.790 --> 00:05:40.800
that

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:42.510
Jesus was crucified on a

00:05:42.520 --> 00:05:44.350
dogwood tree. I don't know how

00:05:44.360 --> 00:05:46.430
people know that unless it

00:05:46.440 --> 00:05:47.830
says it in the Word and I'm just ignorant

00:05:47.830 --> 00:05:47.840
of

00:05:47.840 --> 00:05:50.670
it, but it was

00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:53.150
interesting. I saw dogwood blossoms.

00:05:53.160 --> 00:05:55.470
I knew the Lord, when I heard

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:58.510
the Father say 'dogwood'and 'lamb's

00:05:58.520 --> 00:06:00.230
quarters,

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:02.310
lamb's quarters.'I saw a little

00:06:02.320 --> 00:06:04.510
white flower and I saw the

00:06:04.510 --> 00:06:04.520
lamb.

00:06:04.520 --> 00:06:05.910
Then I

00:06:05.920 --> 00:06:08.950
went in the Spirit to Ireland. The

00:06:08.960 --> 00:06:10.990
Lord said, 'Look at Ireland.'So I was

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:12.350
looking at Ireland and

00:06:12.350 --> 00:06:12.360
thinking,

00:06:12.360 --> 00:06:13.350
'What

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:15.390
are you trying to say about

00:06:15.390 --> 00:06:15.400
this?'A

00:06:15.400 --> 00:06:18.230
lot of people sent Diana and me emails

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:19.070
saying

00:06:19.080 --> 00:06:22.070
dogwood and lamb's quarters are

00:06:22.080 --> 00:06:24.230
for your intestines and

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:26.150
parasites. The

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:28.030
bark

00:06:28.040 --> 00:06:30.070
helps

00:06:30.080 --> 00:06:33.030
your

00:06:33.040 --> 00:06:34.550
stomach problems.

00:06:34.550 --> 00:06:34.560
There

00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:35.950
are

00:06:35.960 --> 00:06:37.870
medicinal

00:06:37.880 --> 00:06:41.430
purposes for these lamb's quarters.

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:42.510
I thought that was

00:06:42.520 --> 00:06:45.190
interesting.

00:06:45.200 --> 00:06:47.030
Praying into that, why is the Lord

00:06:47.040 --> 00:06:49.510
talking about this? He said,

00:06:49.520 --> 00:06:51.750
'Don't take it.'The Lord kept

00:06:51.760 --> 00:06:55.950
saying, 'Don't take it. Don't take it.

00:06:55.960 --> 00:06:58.870
Don't take it.'So I said, 'Don't take

00:06:58.870 --> 00:06:58.880
what?'I

00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:05.150
saw a vial again.

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:13.510
Then somebody gave me Revelation 19.

00:07:13.520 --> 00:07:15.670
Son, could you pull

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:18.070
that up? I believe it was Revelation 19.

00:07:18.080 --> 00:07:20.150
It said the boils come

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:21.590
on the people.

00:07:21.600 --> 00:07:24.390
If mama were

00:07:24.390 --> 00:07:24.400
here—she's busy—but

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:27.230
the scripture talks about in

00:07:27.230 --> 00:07:27.240
Revelation

00:07:27.240 --> 00:07:29.910
the boils coming on

00:07:29.920 --> 00:07:34.630
the people after they take the mark.

00:07:34.640 --> 00:07:38.470
Maybe, just me speaking into it,

00:07:38.480 --> 00:07:41.470
I was having a vision of

00:07:41.470 --> 00:07:41.480
the

00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:43.190
Tribulation again.

00:07:43.200 --> 00:07:44.990
I think it's interesting as we're

00:07:45.000 --> 00:07:46.750
praying because the Lord kept saying, 'Don't

00:07:46.760 --> 00:07:48.030
take it.'Well, don't

00:07:48.040 --> 00:07:50.190
take what? The mark?

00:07:50.200 --> 00:07:53.470
Was it the mark?

00:07:53.480 --> 00:07:54.950
I don't add to or take away from

00:07:54.960 --> 00:07:56.190
anything,

00:07:56.200 --> 00:07:58.030
but I think it's interesting because,

00:07:58.040 --> 00:08:01.350
lately, the

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:06.830
things the Lord is

00:08:06.830 --> 00:08:06.840
showing us—He

00:08:06.840 --> 00:08:09.310
talked about Mystery Babylon

00:08:09.310 --> 00:08:09.320
and

00:08:09.320 --> 00:08:10.950
the major

00:08:10.960 --> 00:08:12.870
shakings that are coming.

00:08:12.880 --> 00:08:14.910
I believe the

00:08:14.920 --> 00:08:17.230
closer we get to the Tribulation, the more

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:19.750
the Lord is letting us see into it

00:08:19.760 --> 00:08:23.110
to pray.

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:25.950
Regardless, I want to say this:

00:08:25.960 --> 00:08:27.390
God wishes that none should

00:08:27.400 --> 00:08:29.750
perish but all come to

00:08:29.750 --> 00:08:29.760
repentance—all

00:08:29.760 --> 00:08:31.750
of us, even the people who are going

00:08:31.760 --> 00:08:33.790
through the Tribulation.

00:08:33.800 --> 00:08:36.029
There's always a way of escaping every

00:08:36.039 --> 00:08:38.589
area of our life. Even to the point of

00:08:38.589 --> 00:08:38.599
praying

00:08:38.599 --> 00:08:40.630
for our brothers and

00:08:40.640 --> 00:08:43.149
sisters who get left—the unbelievers in

00:08:43.149 --> 00:08:43.159
the

00:08:43.159 --> 00:08:45.070
Tribulation. Could we be interceding

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:47.310
for them? I don't doubt it;

00:08:47.320 --> 00:08:49.030
I believe that's how merciful God is.

00:08:49.040 --> 00:08:54.350
But are we getting that close to it?

00:08:54.360 --> 00:08:58.590
I'm telling you, Jesus Christ is coming.

00:08:58.600 --> 00:09:00.950
You must know Him

00:09:00.960 --> 00:09:04.150
as

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:06.230
your Lord and personal Savior. You're

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:08.350
running out of time.

00:09:08.360 --> 00:09:11.550
The urgency of the hour—it's time for

00:09:11.560 --> 00:09:14.710
the Body of Christ to wake up. Jesus is

00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:16.030
coming.

00:09:16.040 --> 00:09:19.790
Many of you are

00:09:19.800 --> 00:09:22.790
asleep; many are not awake for

00:09:22.800 --> 00:09:26.150
what's about to happen on this earth.

00:09:26.160 --> 00:09:28.910
The signs of the times are about to

00:09:28.920 --> 00:09:31.430
heighten, doubling and tripling.

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:32.990
It's like the Lord showing me anointing on

00:09:33.000 --> 00:09:34.750
ministries; they're doubling and

00:09:34.760 --> 00:09:37.270
tripling. If you just spend time with

00:09:37.280 --> 00:09:38.990
the Father

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:41.430
and seek Him daily—not just whenever

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:43.710
it's convenient—finding that intimacy,

00:09:43.720 --> 00:09:46.550
going back to the first love, going back

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:47.510
to

00:09:47.520 --> 00:09:50.070
what you fell in love with,

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:51.750
that tugging at your heart. 'Oh,

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:53.830
Father, how are you today? I want to

00:09:53.840 --> 00:09:55.630
know You more. I want to

00:09:55.640 --> 00:09:57.830
fall more in love with the Lord. Please,

00:09:57.840 --> 00:10:01.310
God, create in me a clean

00:10:01.310 --> 00:10:01.320
heart.'Stripping

00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:03.310
all this stuff off of me that

00:10:03.320 --> 00:10:05.270
would be

00:10:05.270 --> 00:10:05.280
ungodly

00:10:05.280 --> 00:10:07.150
before You.

00:10:07.160 --> 00:10:09.470
What is holding me back from coming to

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:12.030
the greater glory?

00:10:12.040 --> 00:10:14.390
What is it inside of me that

00:10:14.400 --> 00:10:16.150
You see, Lord, that is

00:10:16.160 --> 00:10:19.590
repulsive to You?

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:21.390
To be on that potter's wheel and be

00:10:21.400 --> 00:10:23.590
molded and made every day,

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:26.150
staying from glory to glory to

00:10:26.160 --> 00:10:29.270
cultivate and accelerate.

00:10:32.320 --> 00:10:34.030
The Lord keeps talking to me about

00:10:34.040 --> 00:10:37.630
2026.

00:10:39.520 --> 00:10:41.310
And even, you know, just bringing about

00:10:41.320 --> 00:10:43.470
the alien stuff. I

00:10:43.470 --> 00:10:43.480
am

00:10:43.480 --> 00:10:45.590
telling you, ladies and gentlemen,

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:49.030
great fearful sights you will see that

00:10:49.040 --> 00:10:50.830
will bring you to your knees.

00:10:50.830 --> 00:10:50.840
We are

00:10:50.840 --> 00:10:53.870
about to have great deception

00:10:53.880 --> 00:10:55.750
beyond anybody's comprehension for what we

00:10:55.750 --> 00:10:55.760
are

00:10:55.760 --> 00:10:57.510
about to see. It

00:10:57.510 --> 00:10:57.520
is

00:10:57.520 --> 00:10:59.990
the plan of the enemy. One of the

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:02.829
major things Jesus told me when I went

00:11:02.839 --> 00:11:04.790
to heaven and I was on the edge of it,

00:11:04.800 --> 00:11:07.310
he said to me, "Brandon,

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:09.790
right before I come, one of the major

00:11:09.800 --> 00:11:13.070
things you will see in this earth is

00:11:13.070 --> 00:11:13.080
that

00:11:13.080 --> 00:11:14.430
they

00:11:14.430 --> 00:11:14.440
will

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:17.070
talk about aliens a

00:11:17.070 --> 00:11:17.080
lot."This

00:11:17.080 --> 00:11:18.870
was in

00:11:18.870 --> 00:11:18.880
a

00:11:18.880 --> 00:11:21.070
visitation I had

00:11:21.070 --> 00:11:21.080
on

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:26.150
July 6th of 2014.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:30.550
The Lord said to me, "There will be

00:11:30.560 --> 00:11:32.950
many

00:11:32.960 --> 00:11:34.710
on the news all the time

00:11:34.720 --> 00:11:37.070
talking about aliens,

00:11:40.200 --> 00:11:43.110
ships, and things like that."I heard

00:11:43.120 --> 00:11:44.829
somebody say that Rick Renner was talking

00:11:44.839 --> 00:11:46.990
about the aliens in the water and the

00:11:47.000 --> 00:11:49.350
Nephilim.

00:11:49.360 --> 00:11:51.350
Ladies and gentlemen, it is about

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:53.390
desensitizing you to what is about to

00:11:53.400 --> 00:11:55.829
happen. The main thing the Antichrist

00:11:55.839 --> 00:11:57.790
will say when he comes on the

00:11:57.790 --> 00:11:57.800
scene—when

00:11:57.800 --> 00:12:00.430
I told you he comes before, he stands

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:03.110
in an Oval Office area

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:05.630
with a red carpet behind him.

00:12:05.640 --> 00:12:07.390
Does anybody remember me saying he

00:12:07.400 --> 00:12:11.310
stands in a red carpet area

00:12:11.310 --> 00:12:11.320
with

00:12:11.320 --> 00:12:14.430
all

00:12:14.430 --> 00:12:14.440
these

00:12:14.440 --> 00:12:17.150
lights and the stage, and he tells

00:12:17.160 --> 00:12:18.710
the Christians they were taken because of

